name: GodsDotFun
description: Gods (or GodsDotFun), is a platform building "meme-powered, blockchain-embodied, AI-driven overlords." At the heart of the Gods platform is a commitment to quality. The AI Gods form a curated gallery, each one meticulously crafted and fine-tuned. We need to stand out from the agentic flood of slop. But these gods aren't just for show. These gods won't be aloof and untouchable, but interactive and engaging, ready to "disrupt your timelines, reshape your communities, and demand your offerings."
